# type(scope): subject
#
# Allowed types: feat, fix, chore, refactor, docs, perf, test, build, ci, style
# Scope: optional; e.g. trader, api, logger, web
# Subject: imperative, concise, lowercase, no trailing period

# Body (optional)
# - briefly explain what changed and why
# - if multiple actions, separate with commas or semicolons
# - include context that helps reviewers understand impact

# Footer (optional)
# BREAKING CHANGE: describe what breaks and migration steps
# Refs: issue links or references